Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在海浪聲中一邊欣賞 一邊不斷地眺望著海面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.49,0:00:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會忘卻時光的流逝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人啊還是忙一點好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 忙過頭了也會忘記時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過猶不及 太過忙碌或空閒 都會忘記時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 發呆的時間結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 今天是亞利亞公司的創立紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 就是祖母創立亞利亞公司的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天全天休業
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和艾莉西亞前輩 亞利亞社長三人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去進行我們一直期待的短途旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是自行車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個新布拉諾島上可以騎自行車呢 不過限制在十二歲以下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來AQUA以後還是第一次見到自行車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各式各樣不同顏色風格的房子好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上的布拉諾島也和這裡一樣是個漁村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說 以前捕魚歸來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了漁人在漆黑的霧靄中也能回到自己的家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漁人的妻子們想出辦法 將房子塗上絢麗的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在也還保留著這種傳統呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個是地球時代的威尼斯人大廳中所展示的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被稱作威尼斯網紋的編織品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 說起捕魚 漁網是很重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結網技術發展的結果就是誕生藝術品了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA也繼承了這份技術呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿那件婚紗的新娘一定會十分美麗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上要拜訪的安娜前輩的網紋婚紗裝很驚艷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那位安娜前輩是位什麼樣的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說來 是位開朗並且引人注目的領航員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眾多的男性為她著迷 比起現在的我來說更加忙碌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好厲害的一位前輩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺心跳也加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:53.55,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那段 緩緩流逝的時光中…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這棟房子 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 有人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是出門了嗎？應該沒有弄錯約定的時間呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點問題想問…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有兩個女生在門口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件制服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了 艾莉西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 妳就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面 我叫水無燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳好 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是安娜 這邊的是我家的兒子亞西多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 亞西多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳…妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 怎麼一下子就臉紅啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本沒有臉紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 一被挑撥就上當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 死老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這幅網紋編織真是上品啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奶奶織的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？奶奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我奶奶是這個小鎮有名的網紋編織工藝人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽現在也在那邊學習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還是個生手就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件是結婚時收到的賀禮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的都是自己做的 但是收到的禮物也有不少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩在亞利亞公司工作的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的丈夫 當時在這座小鎮作漁夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他的母親兩人去新威尼斯觀光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後 前輩和深愛母親的漁夫就墜入了愛河
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感謝您能原諒我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 安娜 恭喜妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是件可喜可賀的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳毫不猶豫地走自己的道路 這使我很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝您 祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳 艾莉西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要注意身體哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞公司留下了我的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好軟好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福的婚姻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不盡然呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:07:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 嫁到小島上後也很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和在那之前的領航員生活完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熟人一個也沒有 丈夫總是在外打漁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在島上的人際關係也陷入僵局 很難融入他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時好寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 開始編織網紋的時候 就和島上的人們接觸多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時一件網紋編織品就要分工給五個人做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡和這裡 網紋的刺繡要由不同的人來做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺繡與刺繡之間的連接和邊緣上的刺繡是我的份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:09:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件刺繡是將安娜前輩和島上的人們連接起來的橋樑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 嘴真甜啊 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知祖母身體是否健康呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 阿爾貝特捕魚回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母 您怎麼來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞把我叫過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了 安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到妳精神飽滿的樣子 我很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才在那邊突然遇上的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能見到您真的十分高興啊 祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 亞西多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面 我是阿爾貝特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是水無燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收獲怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 選了些特別好吃的拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那麼 我也得拿出點本事才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤得正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾貝特 吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真豐盛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 別客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚很新鮮 真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您過獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 祖母 請喝點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手藝真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家看上去好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上也是很早出門的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是人來瘋過頭而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡有許多我所不知道的亞利亞公司的歷史呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從亞利亞公司創立伊始的舊人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到最年輕的新進成員 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家聚在一起 總覺得很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞西多也像自己的孫子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 在這裡 發生了名為「這樣聚在一起」的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇蹟…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是多虧祖母創立了亞利亞公司的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是這樣的話 我和阿爾貝特相遇的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 還有生下亞西多的事情都不會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜 妳紮紮實實地走自己的道路 珍惜每天的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算是找到屬於自己的幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞公司並非由我一人之力而建成的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亞利亞社長讓我注意到了這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 應該說是救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長牠？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果方便的話 能說給我們聽聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候 我就快迷失自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我還在姬屋當領航員的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作辛苦了 秋乃前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作辛苦了 秋乃前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時 我還人稱姬屋的王牌 整整14年過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 秋乃前輩 今天仍然亮麗迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅只是從身邊走過 氣氛就為之一變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說 昨天她就「擺平」了6組指名她的客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害 要是我的話絕對累到趴下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然都說歲月不饒人 但是她反而越來越閃耀動人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼忙碌 也不會露出不耐煩的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就是當代第一的水精靈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 玩得真盡興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近 你總是待在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是從哪裡來的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天在這裡幹些什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 迷路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直待在同一個地方 不感到厭倦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 突然問了那麼多問題 你會很困擾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:17:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那段時間裡我雖然也很熱愛工作 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為過於繁忙 周圍的時間流逝得也很快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時候不禁會覺得有點可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這個世界上還有著很多美妙的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望每一件事物都能用心地慢慢培養下去 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總在這裡凝視著什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在等待著什麼重要的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣執著 到底在等什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回過神來的時候 已經是早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明淋了一整晚的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是感到神清氣爽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才察覺到了我一直在勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 我和亞利亞社長 開創了亞利亞公司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想一起看看 牠那美麗的藍色眼睛中顯現的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:20:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（油漆未乾 請注意）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故事就是這樣開場的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將來總有一天 燈里會開始經營亞利亞公司
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們正期待著還不為人所知的屬於燈里的亞利亞公司
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 我加入亞利亞公司 真是非常幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我和這麼溫柔有情的人們在一起過著每一天的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里姐姐 亞利亞公司的美好之處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能在於很多人的感情和願望中揉合了溫柔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.12,0:22:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羨慕妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.28,0:24:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 燈里前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超 超級SOS
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.25,0:24:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎麼啦？愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.81,0:24:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前輩 SOS
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.50,0:24:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.38,0:24:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那份 珍重之人的記憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.20,0:24:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 請握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
